title: Credits

This game was developed by <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/_BrokenArrows/">u/_BrokenArrows</a>. It is a fork from the Autumn Chen's <a href="https://red-autumn.itch.io/petrograd-1917">Petrograd 1917</a>, which if you have not tried out you should! Immediately!
Aside from Petrograd 1917, great inspiration was taken from the original <a href="https://red-autumn.itch.io/social-democracy">Social Democracy, an Alternate History</a> also by Autumn Chen.
Added to that, the acclaimed mod to that game, <a href="https://originn0.github.io/dynamic_social_democracy/">Dynamic Social Democracy</a> by originn0, was invaluable in making this game and all the coding tricks that it uses.

Just as in the originals, many works were referenced in the making of this game.

