Vought, M. (2025). "Nationalism and Ethnic Mobilization: Towards an Integrated Perspective". Cambridge University Press. Available from doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1017/nps.2024.98">doi.org/10.1017/nps.2024.98</a>

